metadata.symbol: A potent and quirky mix of alternative manipulated photography of every stripe and color, continuously made fresh and served up here for your viewing pleasure!
metadata.description: MORBUS (Micro-Macro-26) is a single digital JPG image from a recent project entitled ‘MicroMacro’ where I photographed tiny objects, mostly nails. Many of my works made at this time became visually suggestive of the Covid 19 era. Highly contagious.
